gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 121, Rockets 116
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Rockets, 121-116. Stephen Curry recorded 32 points (5-9 3PM) and five rebounds for the Warriors, with Klay Thompson adding 20 points, three rebounds, and three assists in the victory. Alperen Sengun tallied a season-high 30 points, to go along with 13 rebounds and five assists for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 7-8 in the regular season, while the Rockets fall to 6-6.
